ty dollars. His hand flew to his right side. It was there, slava Bogu (thank God)! Very well! He would not wear his black suit—vot i vsyo (that’s all). He would retrieve it on his way back. He had lost, dumped, shed many more valuable things in his day. Energetically, almost lightheartedly, Pnin boarded the bus.

